#### **1. Largest Contentful Paint (LCP) - Target: <2.5s**
```javascript
// Advanced LCP optimization strategy
class LCPOptimizer {
  constructor() {
    this.criticalResources = [
      'assets/styles.css',
      'assets/profile-preview.png',
      'fonts/inter-400.woff2'
    ];
    this.setupResourcePrioritization();
  }

  setupResourcePrioritization() {
    // Preload critical above-the-fold resources
    const preloadLinks = this.criticalResources.map(resource => {
      const link = document.createElement('link');
      link.rel = 'preload';
      link.href = resource;
      link.as = this.getResourceType(resource);
      if (resource.includes('font')) {
        link.crossOrigin = 'anonymous';
      }
      return link;
    });

    preloadLinks.forEach(link => document.head.appendChild(link));
  }
}
```

**LCP Optimization Techniques**:
- **Critical Resource Preloading**: Hero image and critical CSS prioritization
- **Image Optimization**: WebP format with fallbacks, responsive images
- **Font Loading Strategy**: Font-display swap with FOUT mitigation
- **CSS Critical Path**: Inline critical CSS, defer non-critical styles

#### **2. First Input Delay (FID) - Target: <100ms**
```javascript
// FID optimization through code splitting and lazy loading
class FIDOptimizer {
  constructor() {
    this.setupLazyLoading();
    this.optimizeEventListeners();
  }

  setupLazyLoading() {
    // Lazy load non-critical JavaScript
    const observerOptions = {
      root: null,
      rootMargin: '50px',
      threshold: 0.1
    };

    const lazyObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          this.loadDeferredScript(entry.target.dataset.src);
          lazyObserver.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, observerOptions);

    document.querySelectorAll('[data-lazy-script]').forEach(el => {
      lazyObserver.observe(el);
    });
  }

  optimizeEventListeners() {
    // Passive event listeners for better scroll performance
    document.addEventListener('scroll', this.handleScroll, { passive: true });
    document.addEventListener('touchstart', this.handleTouch, { passive: true });
  }
}
```

**FID Optimization Techniques**:
- **Code Splitting**: Defer non-critical JavaScript loading
- **Event Listener Optimization**: Passive listeners, debounced handlers
- **Third-party Script Management**: Async/defer loading strategies
- **Main Thread Management**: Web Workers for heavy computations

